name: MenusbyNutrislice
0:
”Alexa, launch Nutrislice Menus.”
”My organization is Stony Brook University.”
”My favorite dining location is East Side Dining.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nutrislice menus
Developer Terms of Use
des: Wondering what's for lunch today? Getting the answer has never been easier using Menus by Nutrislice. Simply select your organization and location, then ask Alexa what's on the menu. Nutrislice provides menu information based on which meals your organization has published within our platform.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
